1
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:28,700
 ♫ Heavens strike with thunderous wrath ♫ 

2
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:32,420
 ♫ Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes ♫ 

3
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:35,780
 ♫ Endless splendor
cultivated through lifetimes ♫ 

4
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:40,540
 ♫ Turns to dust between my fingers
in an instant ♫ 

5
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:44,220
 ♫ When the line
between good and evil is clear ♫ 

6
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:48,340
 ♫ Countless souls drift
into the boundless wilds ♫ 

7
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:51,500
 ♫ Carrying the spirit fire forward ♫ 

8
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,580
 ♫ I defy fate ♫ 

9
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:57,060
 ♫ Just to remain by your side ♫ 

10
00:00:57,060 --> 00:01:00,940
 ♫ Falling into love's abyss ♫ 

11
00:01:00,940 --> 00:01:04,780
 ♫ Like heavy rain pouring down ♫ 

12
00:01:04,780 --> 00:01:08,460
 ♫ Drunk on romance ♫ 

13
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:12,300
 ♫ In a blink, love and hate
vanish into illusion ♫ 

14
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:16,300
 ♫ Falling into endless love ♫ 

15
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:19,620
 ♫ Stirring waves upending a lifetime ♫ 

16
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:22,660
 ♫ Even if this life leads to ruin ♫ 

17
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:26,980
 ♫ I still choose to be entangled with you ♫ 

18
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:30,125
 ♫ Through all lifetimes ♫ 

19
00:01:30,125 --> 00:01:36,580
 

20
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:39,620
 

21
00:01:39,620 --> 00:01:42,477
 

22
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:46,080
 The barrier is powerful. 

23
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:49,580
 Looks like the Spirit Fire is inside. 

24
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,740
 A Bloodmist Array. 

25
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:19,770
 A pool filled with the blood
of the Fengshan Clan. 

26
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,890
You are but a guard dog.

27
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,520
 You must promise me 

28
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:49,080
 not to tear open your wounds, stumble, or fall. 

29
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,930
 I'll be worried. 

30
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,740
Come in.

31
00:04:40,790 --> 00:04:42,490
Who are you?

32
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:48,460
Jiao, come in, and I will tell you.

33
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:58,707
 

34
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:17,200
 The Spirit Fire 

35
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,050
 really is here. 

36
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:32,760
Jiao.

37
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,680
You've finally come.

38
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,710
Are you Sima Shi?

39
00:05:36,710 --> 00:05:39,010
I've been waiting for you.

40
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,390
So, you didn't die
in the fire at White Deer Cliff.

41
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:46,120
So, E did as I asked

42
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:49,050
and merged the Spirit Fire with you.

43
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:53,250
I am so glad that you managed to pull through.

44
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,440
I'll get you out of here.

45
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,520
Don't bother.

46
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:05,370
I didn't wait for you
because I wanted to leave.

47
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:08,790
With this broken body of mine,

48
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:10,960
I could never leave again.

49
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:13,590
I lingered here, waiting,

50
00:06:13,590 --> 00:06:17,660
just to tell you
what really happened back then.

51
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:24,270
The ascension curse
made the Sima clan dwindle further.

52
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:26,880
We, despite our precious blood,

53
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:32,200
fell from leaders
to mere tools of the Eight Palaces.

54
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,130
By my generation,

55
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:38,150
all freedom had been lost.

56
00:06:38,150 --> 00:06:43,520
To produce a more refined Fengshan bloodline
to nourish the Spirit Fire,

57
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:46,830
the Eight Palaces forced
your mother and me into marriage.

58
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:48,960
Soon after,

59
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:53,590
you, with the purest Fengshan atavistic blood,

60
00:06:53,590 --> 00:06:55,960
were born.

61
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:58,910
Seeing such purity,

62
00:06:58,910 --> 00:07:01,660
the greed of the Eight Palaces

63
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:04,270
grew insatiable.

64
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:06,320
They wanted more offspring of this bloodline,

65
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:09,150
so they sealed your mother and me
in White Deer Cliff.

66
00:07:09,150 --> 00:07:12,440
 The Sima clan must remain here
to guard the Spirit Fire. 

67
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:16,230
 Grandmaster, please stay on White Deer Cliff. 

68
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:18,590
 You are treating us like prisoners! 

69
00:07:18,590 --> 00:07:21,930
 Do you even have
the slightest respect for us Grandmasters? 

70
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:27,960
I had intended to merge
with the Fengshan Spirit Fire

71
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:30,710
so that I could gain its power

72
00:07:30,710 --> 00:07:33,320
and put an end to their scheme.

73
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,880
But the Spirit Fire was too powerful.

74
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:39,080
I could not endure the agony

75
00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:42,420
and even fell into madness at one point.

76
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:45,400
In the end,

77
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,050
I had to give up.

78
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:52,130
And even knowing the pain,

79
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,680
you still chose to have me
merge with the Spirit Fire?

80
00:07:56,680 --> 00:08:00,320
I... I had no other choice.

81
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:03,640
With your rare and pure
Fengshan atavistic blood,

82
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:06,200
you could withstand the Spirit Fire

83
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:09,440
and become the first
to break the ascension curse.

84
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:12,680
But during the fusion, we realized

85
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:15,230
that your blood was so pure

86
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:19,080
that you needed
a stronger Spirit Fire to merge with.

87
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:22,710
Otherwise, your blood would devour

88
00:08:22,710 --> 00:08:26,150
the Spirit Fire entirely during the fusion.

89
00:08:26,150 --> 00:08:31,320
So, the other Sima clansmen and I

90
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,680
made a collective decision.

91
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:37,280
 If our deaths can help Jiao
successfully merge with the Spirit Fire, 

92
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:40,230
 the Eight Palaces won't dare
to harm the Sima clan! 

93
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:42,200
 - That's right!
- We'll help Jiao merge with the Spirit Fire! 

94
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,110
 - Me too!
- Yes, me too! 

95
00:08:44,110 --> 00:08:47,590
 - Me too!
- I'm in! 

96
00:08:47,590 --> 00:08:50,320
The Sima clan no longer
allowed themselves to be pawns

97
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:53,440
for the greed of the Eight Palaces.

98
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:57,710
So, we decided to feed
the Spirit Fire with our blood

99
00:08:57,710 --> 00:09:00,320
to form a Spirit Fire strong enough

100
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,750
for you to merge with.

101
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:07,710
But once the blood sacrifice began,

102
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:11,960
we found that the Spirit Fire
was like a bottomless pit.

103
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:18,590
Over a hundred clansmen gave their lives
one after another.

104
00:09:18,590 --> 00:09:20,940
Not a single one gave up.

105
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:23,180
In the end,

106
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:28,220
the clansmen poured
every drop of their blood into it

107
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:33,290
and finally formed
the most powerful Spirit Fire in existence.

108
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:36,770
Sacrificing the entire clan

109
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:43,510
and leaving such a heavy burden on a child...

110
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:45,830
Should I call you pitiable, or despicable?

111
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:48,960
If we had to choose again,

112
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:51,860
we would still walk the same path.

113
00:10:00,590 --> 00:10:02,960
Then why are you here?

114
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:06,800
I feared the Eight Palaces
would figure out our plan,

115
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:09,750
so I feigned madness and set a fire,

116
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:12,750
making them believe I had gone insane

117
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:14,800
and burned the whole clan alive.

118
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:17,740
The final step for merging
the Spirit Fire into you

119
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:23,980
required your mother to absorb it for you.

120
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:29,740
I thought our plan would end there.

121
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,400
 He's dead. 

122
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,800
 Oh, no. Where is Sima E? 

123
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:48,040
 - Hurry! 
- But in the fire at White Deer Cliff,

124
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:50,800
a spy the Shi family had planted
in the Eight Palaces

125
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:53,830
found me, barely alive,

126
00:10:53,830 --> 00:10:58,160
and secretly took me away.

127
00:10:58,160 --> 00:11:00,960
At first, the Shi family
truly meant to save me.

128
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:03,830
But once I was rescued,
I was desperate to find you,

129
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:06,470
and from me, Shi Yong You learned

130
00:11:06,470 --> 00:11:09,060
the secret of how to break the ascension curse.

131
00:11:09,990 --> 00:11:13,110
That greed consumed him.

132
00:11:13,110 --> 00:11:16,280
Shi Yong You and his disciple, Shi Qian Lv,

133
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,560
stole a dying flame of the Spirit Fire's avatar

134
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:21,710
from White Deer Cliff

135
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:25,440
and used my body as the wick to keep it alive,

136
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,080
and at the same time...

137
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,700
At the same time...

138
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:32,280
Shi Yong You and Shi Qian Lv

139
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:34,110
secretly built Baifeng Mountain,

140
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:36,160
gathering the blood of the Fengshan Clan

141
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:38,890
to feed that Spirit Fire.

142
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,060
Exactly.

143
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:44,510
Now that you've come here,

144
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:47,470
it is time for all of this to end.

145
00:11:47,470 --> 00:11:50,230
Jiao, remember this.

146
00:11:50,230 --> 00:11:52,400
We are the Fengshan Clan.

147
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:56,510
The Fengshan Clan is born extraordinary,

148
00:11:56,510 --> 00:11:58,680
destined to share life with heaven and earth.

149
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:00,650
Share life with heaven and earth?

150
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:03,990
Look around you.

151
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:08,400
Now the Sima clan has only me left.

152
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:11,080
So what if there is only you left?

153
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:14,870
As long as you can live
for tens of thousands of years,

154
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:16,630
as long as you don't die,

155
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:18,680
the Fengshan Clan will never vanish,

156
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:22,960
and the glory may one day be ours again.

157
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:25,230
Consume this Spirit Fire,

158
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:27,890
and not only will your wounds heal,

159
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:33,180
but you will also have
two Spirit Fires inside you.

160
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,740
But beyond becoming stronger,

161
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:40,230
there is another possibility.

162
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:43,110
If I consume it,

163
00:12:43,110 --> 00:12:45,530
the Spirit Fire might reduce me
to ash in an instant.

164
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,510
Isn't that right?

165
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:54,340
You carry the atavistic Fengshan bloodline,
a marvel unseen in ages.

166
00:12:55,560 --> 00:13:00,650
You can accomplish what none of us ever could.

167
00:13:01,780 --> 00:13:06,260
 ♫ I'd bear no resentment or regret ♫ 

168
00:13:06,260 --> 00:13:11,660
 ♫ Let my mortal heart fall to the human world ♫ 

169
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:18,900
 ♫ I'll trade it for a lone, fearless self
and let the past drift away ♫ 

170
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:25,660
 ♫ With every regret I once held onto ♫ 

171
00:13:25,660 --> 00:13:31,780
 ♫ I'll survive countless trials
and tribulations ♫ 

172
00:13:32,740 --> 00:13:38,500
 ♫ Let my mortal heart sink into the sea ♫ 

173
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:45,380
 ♫ I dream of a weightless self,
soaring to the heavens ♫ 

174
00:13:45,380 --> 00:13:48,780
 ♫ Neither alive nor gone,
I'm bound only by endless loneliness ♫ 

175
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:52,140
 ♫ Watching the world change ♫ 

176
00:13:52,140 --> 00:14:04,500
 ♫ Yet still unable
to see through the long night ♫ 

177
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:10,180
Now your wish is fulfilled.

178
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:30,320
There's trouble at Taiwei Mountain.

179
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:33,980
Sect Master, Madam Ye sent word
that Liao Ting Yan had been found.

180
00:14:35,160 --> 00:14:38,470
Order Ye Ru Ling to seize her
and bring her to Taixuan Peak at once.

181
00:14:38,470 --> 00:14:42,200
Otherwise, all her clansmen
at Yin Palace will die.

182
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,490
Understood.

183
00:14:46,830 --> 00:14:48,830
I can sense that something

184
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:51,080
has happened to the Spirit Fire
at Taiwei Mountain.

185
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:54,700
Sima Jiao may have already found it.

186
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:57,200
I'll go there first to check.

187
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:59,200
Notify the palace heads
to gather at Taixuan Peak

188
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,710
and set up an array.

189
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:03,590
Once Sima Jiao shows himself
at Taiwei Mountain,

190
00:15:03,590 --> 00:15:07,160
I will use Liao Ting Yan
to draw him to Taixuan Peak.

191
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:11,830
Then, the palace heads
will capture him together.

192
00:15:11,830 --> 00:15:13,100
Understood.

193
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:30,800
Could this mean something unexpected

194
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:32,770
will happen to Sima Jiao?

195
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:40,220
What kind of fool
curses her own cultivation partner?

196
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:43,080
He's so powerful.

197
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:45,700
No one in this world could kill him.

198
00:15:46,590 --> 00:15:48,710
He might suffer a small injury,

199
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:51,110
but nothing serious will happen.

200
00:15:51,110 --> 00:15:53,740
If only I still had the Transvision Mirror.

201
00:15:54,470 --> 00:15:56,750
Then Jiao would be able to tell me he's safe.

202
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:58,560
Ru Ling!

203
00:15:58,560 --> 00:16:00,060
 Nian Jiu? 

204
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:06,080
Ru Ling!

205
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,580
Ru Ling!

206
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:09,990
Nian Jiu!

207
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:11,470
Ting Yan!

208
00:16:11,470 --> 00:16:12,800
Ting Yan!

209
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:14,180
Capture her!

210
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:25,830
Madam Ye, I didn't expect us
to meet again so soon.

211
00:16:25,830 --> 00:16:28,230
How did you even find me?

212
00:16:28,230 --> 00:16:29,590
In the Immortal Realm,

213
00:16:29,590 --> 00:16:31,960
only I can recognize the traces
of your extreme-cold nature.

214
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,560
Your cultivation has advanced rapidly lately,

215
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:36,680
and the traces have become clearer than ever.

216
00:16:36,680 --> 00:16:40,530
So, I should thank you for not coming
to capture me sooner?

217
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:44,750
The Sect Master said

218
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:46,350
that if we could not catch Sima Jiao,

219
00:16:46,350 --> 00:16:48,890
we must at least bring Liao Ting Yan back.

220
00:16:54,110 --> 00:16:55,630
Ting Yan!

221
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:56,640
Ting Yan!

222
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:58,100
You're courting death!

223
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:03,560
Madam Ye, whose side are you really on?

224
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:06,310
How dare you, a mere disciple, question me?

225
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:09,710
Yes, Sect Master Shi ordered you to watch me,

226
00:17:09,710 --> 00:17:12,310
but he didn't tell you to command me,

227
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:16,230
and I certainly don't need
to explain my decisions to you.

228
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:18,270
Let's get back to business.

229
00:17:18,270 --> 00:17:19,660
Take her away!

230
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:22,960
- Move.
- Let her go!

231
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:25,470
Ting Yan! Ting Yan!

232
00:17:25,470 --> 00:17:27,090
Let me out!

233
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,470
Ru Ling!

234
00:17:30,470 --> 00:17:32,030
Let Ting Yan go!

235
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:33,530
Ru Ling!

236
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:43,050
My Spirit Fire...

237
00:17:57,070 --> 00:17:58,990
You are finally here.

238
00:17:58,990 --> 00:18:00,790
You absorbed my Spirit Fire!

239
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:05,360
Centuries of planning,
and you walked away with the prize.

240
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:10,360
Sima Jiao, you vile, despicable man!

241
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:11,900
I am flattered.

242
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:25,473
 

243
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:37,790
Sima Jiao harmed my daughter,
causing me endless pain.

244
00:18:37,790 --> 00:18:42,330
Now, I'll make him taste the same.

245
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,740
How can this be?

246
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:59,230
She has such powerful defenses.

247
00:18:59,230 --> 00:19:01,030
I can't wound her at all.

248
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:03,200
Madam Yue, we're against a strong enemy.

249
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:04,600
Don't act rashly.

250
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:08,120
Madam Yue, if anyone here destroys this tool

251
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:10,230
meant for the capture of Sima Jiao,

252
00:19:10,230 --> 00:19:11,640
I will have to treat them as a saboteur

253
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:13,070
of the Eight Palaces' grand plan.

254
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:17,010
Ye Ru Ling, whose side are you really on?

255
00:19:18,360 --> 00:19:22,440
Even now, you still have sympathy
for Liao Ting Yan, don't you?

256
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:25,230
Madam Yue, now is not the time
for personal grudges.

257
00:19:25,230 --> 00:19:27,030
We must focus on our task.

258
00:19:27,030 --> 00:19:28,990
Master Ri is right.

259
00:19:28,990 --> 00:19:31,750
Fellow palace heads, there is no time to waste.

260
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:33,140
Let's form the array.

261
