394
00:32:52,840 --> 00:32:55,220
 Your soul must still be here. 

395
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,860
 I will find it. 

396
00:32:58,860 --> 00:33:04,060
 ♫ I still choose to be entangled with you ♫ 

