- How are things at the front?

399
00:33:21,790 --> 00:33:24,270
Hundreds of demon soldiers
have invaded the front line.

400
00:33:24,270 --> 00:33:25,510
They will soon reach here.

401
00:33:25,510 --> 00:33:28,440
Hundreds? Even with the disciples
from the reserve force,

402
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:31,070
we only have a few dozen soldiers here.

403
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:34,470
Master Yuan, please place
all remaining forces under my command.

404
00:33:34,470 --> 00:33:35,710
Together with Hei Nian Jiu,

405
00:33:35,710 --> 00:33:37,960
