408
00:33:48,030 --> 00:33:49,790
We've cultivated for so long.

409
00:33:49,790 --> 00:33:52,600
If we die now protecting the Celestial Palace,

410
00:33:52,600 --> 00:33:54,770
it will be a worthwhile death.

411
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:56,960
