412
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:59,990
Everyone, protect the Grandmaster!

413
00:33:59,990 --> 00:34:01,660
Yes, General!

414
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:49,180
The Spirit Fire? It's the Grandmaster.

415
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:52,500
Did you really think I was dead?

416
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:08,280
Greetings, Grandmaster!

417
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:10,450
 Greetings, Grandmaster! 

418
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:17,030
Grandmaster.

419
00:35:17,030 --> 00:35:19,880
Grandmaster, you're awake.

420
00:35:25,680 --> 00:35:27,070
Why are you crying?

421
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:33,220
Grandmaster, have the two Spirit Fires
in your body completely merged?

422
00:35:37,110 --> 00:35:38,500
Where's Ting Yan?

423
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:41,110
Have you found her?

424
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:44,410
Grandmaster, have you forgotten?

425
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:48,240
Ting Yan left behind no fragments

426
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:50,150
of her soul at all.

427
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:52,990
She cannot be reborn.

428
00:35:52,990 --> 00:35:54,770
And Ru Ling...

429
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:57,970
She met the same fate.

430
00:36:06,990 --> 00:36:09,240
What about the Shi clan?

431
00:36:09,240 --> 00:36:12,030
After the battle at Taiwei Mountain,

432
00:36:12,030 --> 00:36:14,550
the Shi clan was nearly annihilated.

433
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:17,320
But we searched every corner
of the Celestial Palace

434
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:19,550
and never found Shi Qian Lv's body.

435
00:36:19,550 --> 00:36:21,920
I believe he must be living under another name,

436
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:24,240
hiding somewhere in the Celestial Palace.

437
00:36:24,240 --> 00:36:26,450
Having caused such upheaval,

438
00:36:27,550 --> 00:36:29,890
Shi Qian Lv cannot remain here.

439
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:35,110
The breaches in the barrier

440
00:36:35,110 --> 00:36:37,550
were perfect for him to escape.

441
00:36:37,550 --> 00:36:39,320
Grandmaster, are you saying...

442
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:40,850
We'll go to the Demon Realm

443
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:43,960
to root out the trouble.

444
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:47,150
Grandmaster, though my medical skills
are modest,

445
00:36:47,150 --> 00:36:51,670
I beg to accompany you
to safeguard your health.

446
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:54,030
Grandmaster, you have only just awakened.

447
00:36:54,030 --> 00:36:56,020
Are you sure about this?

448
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,960
Do you object?

449
00:36:58,960 --> 00:37:00,630
I wouldn't dare.

450
00:37:00,630 --> 00:37:03,280
But I have one request.

451
00:37:03,280 --> 00:37:05,030
