460
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:47,510
This isn't your fault, Grandmaster.

461
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:50,960
Back then, the Immortal-Demon Barrier
was suddenly destroyed.

462
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:52,110
And after you fell into slumber,

463
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:54,630
the Demon Lord set his sights on our territory.

464
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:56,930
That's why so many lives were lost.

465
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:11,030
Grandmaster, did you just mend
the Immortal-Demon Barrier?

466
00:38:11,030 --> 00:38:13,470
The Grandmaster doesn't seem
as fearsome as the rumors say.

467
00:38:13,470 --> 00:38:15,990
The Grandmistress was kind, gentle,
and disliked bloodshed.

468
00:38:15,990 --> 00:38:17,960
It was because of her that he changed.

469
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:20,100
What a pity that fate was so cruel.

470
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:33,665
 

