473
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:45,880
When will I be reborn?

474
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:49,550
My lord, in the Demon Realm, White Bone Abyss
holds the richest demonic energy.

475
00:38:49,550 --> 00:38:51,510
Please rest and recuperate here.

476
00:38:51,510 --> 00:38:52,760
Don't worry, my lord.

477
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:55,190
Everything is ready
for the restoration of your soul.

478
00:38:55,190 --> 00:38:58,360
Now we only need Sima Jiao's Fengshan blood.

479
00:38:58,360 --> 00:39:00,840
He's slept for 18 years.

480
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:02,800
18 years have passed,

481
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:06,670
and you still haven't brought him to me?
 

482
00:39:06,670 --> 00:39:09,990
My lord, he has awakened recently,

483
00:39:09,990 --> 00:39:13,550
