the two Spirit Fires.

484
00:39:13,550 --> 00:39:15,060
Useless fool!

485
00:39:16,990 --> 00:39:18,590
Please calm your anger, my lord.

486
00:39:18,590 --> 00:39:19,630
We still have the Frost Fish.

487
00:39:19,630 --> 00:39:21,510
She can kill him and take his blood.

488
00:39:21,510 --> 00:39:25,190
You have searched for her
for so many years without success.

489
00:39:25,190 --> 00:39:27,320
She must already be dead.

490
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:30,190
No, I'm sure she is still alive.

491
00:39:30,190 --> 00:39:33,070
The traces of her extreme-cold nature
left at the Immortal-Demon Barrier's breaches

492
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:36,110
were proof that she passed through the barrier
into the Demon Realm

493
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:37,990
during the great disaster 18 years ago.

494
00:39:37,990 --> 00:39:41,150
But she must have been gravely injured,

495
00:39:41,150 --> 00:39:43,240
which is why we haven't been able
to track her down.

496
00:39:43,240 --> 00:39:46,320
There is only one Frost Fish in existence.

497
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:49,760
She is the perfect weapon to kill Sima Jiao.

498
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:51,880
